# 詞: 睇怕

1. 睇怕今日落大雨，我哋要改期去行山。 (It looks like it's going to rain heavily today, so we'll have to reschedule our hiking trip.)
2. 佢成日唔返屋企，睇怕係喺外面玩緊。 (He never comes home; it seems he's out playing.)
3. 睇怕呢單生意搞唔掂，我哋要諗下後路。 (It looks like this deal won't work out; we need to think of a backup plan.)
4. 佢面色好差，睇怕係病緊。 (He looks very unwell; it seems he's sick.)
5. 睇怕呢部車要換新嘅，舊嘅已經壞咗好多。 (It looks like this car needs to be replaced; the old one has broken down too many times.)
6. 佢唔肯講真話，睇怕有啲嘢瞞住我哋。 (He won't tell the truth; it seems he's hiding something from us.)
7. 睇怕呢個計劃要延遲，因為資金未到位。 (It looks like this plan will be delayed because the funding hasn't arrived yet.)
8. 佢成日遲到，睇怕係唔重視呢份工。 (He's always late; it seems he doesn't value this job.)
9. 睇怕呢場比賽我哋贏唔到，對手太強。 (It looks like we won't win this match; the opponent is too strong.)
10. 佢成日唔接電話，睇怕係有事發生。 (He never answers his phone; it seems something has happened.) [end of text]


